channel.title: Comments on: Ceramic Coating with Auto Werks Detailing

item.title: By: Jasmine Paulos
item.dc:creator: Jasmine Paulos
item.description: Your car is looking super duper shiny. I am really impressed. Black color has brought such a rich look to your car with that ceramic coat. Thank you for sharing your experience. I am really in love with your car, I must appreciate you for this work. You have done a wonderful job, I must say.
